translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  5,51,"Oh nina enikholwayo! Ningathathi amaJuda namaKhrestu ukuba babe abangane (abasizi noma abavikeli) abanye babo bangabangane babanye futhi noma ngabe ngubani kunina obathatha njengabangane ngakho-ke ngempela yena ungomunye wabo, ngempela uMvelinqangi akabaholi abantu abayizoni"
  5,52,"Ngakho-ke uyababona labo ezinhliziyweni zabo okunesifo bajahe kubona bathi, “siyesaba hleze sehlelwe yishwa kodwa mhlawumbe uMvelinqangi uzoletha ukunqoba noma isinqumo esivela kuyena ngakho-ke bayozisola ngenxa yalokho abakufihla okusemiphefumulweni yabo"
  5,53,"Futhi labo abakholwayo bayothi, “laba bayilabo abafunga ngoMvelinqangi izifungo zabo ezinzima ukuthi ngempela bona babekanye nani, imisebenzi yabo iphenduka ize leze baphenduka abalahlekelweyo"
  5,54,"Oh nina enikholwayo! Noma ngabe ngubani kunina obuyela emumva ayeke inkolo yakhe (yobu Islam) ngakho-ke uMvelinqangi uyoletha abantu ayobathanda nabo bamthande, ukuzithoba kwabakholwayo, amandla okubhekana nabangakholwa, bazabalaza endleleni kaMvelinqangi futhi abesabiukugxekwaabagxeki, lokhokungumusakaMvelinqangi uwunika lowo amthandayo futhi uMvelinqangi ungamele konke uyazi"
  5,55,"Kuphela, umvikeli wenu nguMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe nalabo abakholwa nalabo abenza umthandazo futhi bakhokha izakaah\tfuthi\tbona\tbengabakhothamayo\t(ekukhonzeni uMvelinqangi)"
  5,56,FuthinomangabengubaniothathauMvelinqanginesithunywa sakhe nalabo abakholwayo njengabasizi ngakho-ke ngempela bona engxenyeni kaMvelinqangi bayoba ngabanqobayo
  5,57,Oh nina enikholwayo! Ningathathi labo abenza inkolo yenu inhlekisa nomdlalo kulabo ababenikwe incwadi ngaphambilini kwenu nabangakholwa ukuba babengabasizi (abangane) futhi sabani uMvelinqangi uma nina ningabakholwayo